{
  "info": {
    "name": "OCP — Discussions Module",
    "description": "Online Course Platform — Discussions Module API\n\nPhase 4: Хэлэлцүүлгийн нийтлэл (Discussion Posts) + Хичээлийн сэтгэгдэл (Lesson Comments)\n\n## Хэрэглэх дараалал\n1. Auth → Student, Teacher, Admin нэвтрэх\n2. Setup → Сургалт + хичээл үүсгэх + нийтлэх + элсэлт\n3. Discussion Posts → Create → List → Get → Update → Reply → Vote → Accept → Pin → Lock → Flag → Delete\n4. Lesson Comments → Create → List → Update → Reply → Upvote → Delete\n\n## Урьдчилсан нөхцөл\n- DB-д STUDENT, TEACHER, ADMIN role-тэй хэрэглэгчид бүртгэлтэй байх\n- Published сургалт + published хичээлүүд байх\n- Student enrollment ACTIVE байх\n\n## Variables\n- `baseUrl`: API URL (default: http://localhost:3001/api/v1)\n- `studentToken`: STUDENT JWT\n- `teacherToken`: TEACHER JWT\n- `adminToken`: ADMIN JWT\n- `courseId`: Published сургалтын ID\n- `lessonId`: Хичээлийн ID\n- `postId`: Нийтлэлийн ID\n- `replyId`: Хариултын ID\n- `commentId`: Сэтгэгдлийн ID",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3001/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "studentToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "teacherToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
